dsDescriptionValue.value:
Ecosystem service baseline maps for the Volta basin generated by the WaterWorld model v 2.92.

Details:

Baseline analysis representing land cover 2010 and mean climate (climatology) 1950-2010 at 1km spatial resolution for the Volta catchment.  All files are ARCASCII grids Geographic Coordinate System WGS84 Datum. Citation is with each file. The Monthly folder contains data for each month of the climatology, the Annual folder contains annual totals or annual mean maps.  

Users can generate up to date maps themselves  at www.policysupport.org/waterworld using the latest data and algorithms and downloading the outputs.
